   COMPUTERS-NORRIS-COLUMN (Undated) _ Computers have driven this
economy to the longest expansion ever. Computer stocks have racked
up some of the biggest gains of the bull market. But all good
things must end someday, and the signs are growing that the end may
be here. By Floyd Norris.
</P>
