   WITH: PUBLISHING NOTES -- David Hackworth is the most decorated
soldier since Audie Murphy. He also is one of the military's
harshest critics. With nonfiction books such as his memoir ``About
Face'' and ``Hazardous Duty,'' Hackworth is now taking a different
tack; he's trying fiction. (O'Briant, Atlanta Journal Constitution)
</P>
