   WITH: SKUBE ON BOOKS -- ``Change Me Into Zeus's Daughter'' is a
woman's story of overcoming poverty, an alcoholic father and the
childhood shame of facial disfigurement. (Skube, Atlanta Journal
Constitution)
</P>
