Jason Kidd of the U.S. is surrounded by Sarunas Jasikevicius, right
and Ramunas Siskauskas of Lithuania during the second hald of their
Olympic semifinals match, Friday. In a game that wasn't decided
until the final shot missed by about a foot, the United States
edged Lithuania 85-83 Friday night to reach the gold medal game.
(Chang W. Lee/The New York Times)
</P>
<P>
