Kevin Garnett of the United States reacts to a foul called against
him as teammate Vince Carter, left, looks on, Friday during the
men's basketball semifinals against Lithuania. In a game that
wasn't decided until the final shot missed by about a foot, the
United States edged Lithuania 85-83 Friday night to reach the gold
