but the Suharto story is the talk of Indonesia, from the elite
classes to the very poor. Many seem willing to forgive the former
Indonesian leader his crimes, but they are still upset that the
trial did not go forward. The attorney general and human rights
groups say they will press ahead and go after other of Suharto's
family members. By Calvin Sims.
