<P>
   &QL;  PA Contract Awards By Jimmy Chuang States News Service
Washington, September 29 -- Bulova Technologies LLC of Lancaster
won a $189,637 contract from the U.S. Army in Picatinny Arsenal,
N.J., for mortar cartridges.
</P>
