costs and a seasonal travel slowdown take effect this fall, but
overall demand remains strong despite two fuel surcharges this
year. (Fonti, The Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   RETAIL _ Escalating oil prices and consumer debt will add up to
