</P>
<P>
   TRANSPORTATION _ Steep increases in diesel prices and a growing
list of other problems are deflating prospects at trucking firms
that haul most consumer items. (Grantham, The Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   DEPOT-GP _ Home Depot and GP still battling the slump in demand
for building supplies. (Bond, The Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   DOW-QUARTER _ A look ahead at the market and a wrapup of the
