find themselves at a critical juncture. The Bulldogs face a
difficult situation at Arkansas after having lost to South Carolina
and with Tennessee just over the horizon. Tech is 0-2 in the ACC
and can'''t afford to lose at N.C. (Barnhart, Atlanta
