<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   YUGOSLAVIA-ETHNIC (Pristina, Yugoslavia) _ To ethnic Albanians
in Kosovo, a move toward democracy in Yugoslavia is bad news. The
more responsible, internationally recognized government there is in
Belgrade, the less chance the independence-minded ethnic Albanians
have of a permanent, official break from Belgrade. By Kevin Cullen.
1220 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; POLITICS (p) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   SOFT-MONEY (Washington) _ In a year when campaign finance
overhaul was a major topic of the primaries, the general election
