   SCORCHED EARTH _ Clearing minefields is difficult enough without
robotic landmines that hop into gaps in minefields that have been
cleared. To make anti-tank minefields tougher to cross without
anti-personnel mines _ banned under the Ottawa Convention _ the
United States plans to use ``intelligent'' minefields instead. 600
words. By Ian Sample.
