<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-29 16:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6898 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-DYING-LANGUAGES-NYT &LR;      09-29 1207
