   NBC-DEBATE (Washington) _ NBC, under fire for an earlier
decision to pre-empt the first presidential debate for baseball,
said Friday that local TV stations will have the option of
broadcasting next Tuesday's showdown between Republican George W.
Bush and Democrat Al Gore or the previously scheduled playoff game.
(Summary from wires.) By Peter Marks.
